---
// InteractiveCards.astro
---

<section class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-12">
        ¿Cómo podemos <span class="font-semibold text-[#1B365D]">ayudarte a mejorar tu vida</span>?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
        <!-- Tarjeta 1 -->
        <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95">
                ¿Quieres dormir mejor?
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100">
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
                    <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
                        Sabías que el 6,7% de la población española está oficialmente diagnosticada de ansiedad
                    </p>
                </div>
                <button class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px]">
                    Quiero dormir mejor
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta 2 -->
        <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95">
                ¿Necesitas un plus de energía?
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100">
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
                    <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
                        La falta de energía puede afectar significativamente tu calidad de vida
                    </p>
                </div>
                <button class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px]">
                    Quiero más energía
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta 3 -->
        <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95">
                ¿Quieres cuidar tu salud digestiva y evitar que tu estómago te pese?
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100">
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
                    <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
                        Una buena digestión es clave para tu bienestar general
                    </p>
                </div>
                <button class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px]">
                    Mejorar mi digestión
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta 4 -->
        <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95">
                ¿Quieres mejorar tu salud íntima?
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100">
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
                    <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
                        Tu salud íntima merece atención y cuidado especial
                    </p>
                </div>
                <button class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px]">
                    Cuidar mi salud íntima
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta 5 -->
        <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95">
                ¿Te gustaría mejorar tus niveles de estrés y ansiedad?
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100">
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
                    <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
                        El manejo del estrés es fundamental para una vida saludable
                    </p>
                </div>
                <button class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px]">
                    Reducir mi estrés
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .perspective {
        perspective: 1000px;
    }
    
    .transform-style {
        transform-style: preserve-3d;
    }
</style>